    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure, you've found it! This car has been such a joy to own\u2014it runs like a dream and has been really well-cared for. It shows a few tiny signs of being loved, but it's in overall great shape and is super dependable for daily driving. It's a fantastic find for someone who wants a quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
