    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1997 Toyota Supra Turbo features the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six mated to the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The powertrain delivers linear boost through the factory sequential setup, while the rear-end utilizes a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. The chassis exhibits high torsional rigidity, and the suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from recent bushing replacements. Though it shows light cosmetic wear consistent with an enthusiast-driven vehicle, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression across all banks and synchro engagement\u2014are excellent. A turn-key performance icon for the discerning driver.",
